   <p>(Screen.) The Schreyder Monument from St. Sebald at Nuremberg, executed by Adam Kraft in <datestruct value="1492--"><year reg="1492">1492</year></datestruct>.   The reliefs represent the Cross Bearing, the Entombment, and the Resurrection. 
  <p>*Portions of the wrought-iron Screen in Hampton Court gardens, executed by <hi rend=italics>Huntingdon Shaw</hi> of Nottingham, in <datestruct value="1625--"><year reg="1625">1625</year></datestruct>. 
