   <p>Passing the central <hi rend=italics>Screen</hi> of the court, we see- 
   <QUOTE rend=blockquote><p>The Chimney-piece of the Council Chamber of the Palais de Justice, Bruges, <datestruct value="1529--"><year reg="1529">1529</year></datestruct>. 
